  "ComponentType": "Bluetooth Audio System-on-Chip (SoC) with integrated DSP, Audio Codec, and PMU",
  "Description": "The AC6955F4 is a highly integrated Bluetooth audio SoC designed for stereo headsets. It features a 240MHz 32-bit DSP with FPU for audio processing, a Bluetooth 5.1 BR/EDR/BLE radio, a multi-format audio decoder (including SBC, AAC, MP3, FLAC), and a complete audio codec with DAC, ADC, and microphone interfaces. It integrates a full-speed USB OTG controller and a rich set of peripherals (UART, SPI, I2C, PWM, SD host) into a QSOP24 package, targeting low-power portable audio applications.",
